        "subject": "LU-1043 clio: report error when ost object is missing",
        "message": "LU-1043 clio: report error when ost object is missing\n\nIn cl_glimpse_lock(), the return value of cl_merge_lvb() is missed,\nwhich result in no error reported on size glimpse even when some\nost object is mssing.\n\nThis patch fixed the problem and added a test case for it.\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <niu@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ifd4c7fefe4253599550fd3f485043252ba710d41\n"
      },
